<plot>Life journey of Uruguayan born poet, composer, and painter Mauricio Saravia, who was diagnosed at the age of five with McCune-Albright syndrome. The successful artist describes a lifetime of struggle against the incurable, rare, and painful disease which atrophies the growth of bones and affects the pigmentation of the skin.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?477809</url></doc>
